## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on a limited number of sources, primarily from Harvard Business Review and related PDFs. While these sources are authoritative, the scope of the findings could be broadened by incorporating additional perspectives from industry reports and case studies. Furthermore, the data is based on publications up to 2015, which may not fully capture the latest advancements and trends in smart, connected products.

